tweet: The impact of doing away with the  essential commodities act  is eroding livelihoods further.  Onion prices are skyrocketing. There are no restraints on traders and corporates to create artificial shortages & reap super profits.  Modi government must enforce price controls.  https://t.co/fCrV3N4HtQ
name: Sitaram Yechury

tweet: Stock limits imposed to control onion price rise. With such 1970s instincts, how can Modi Govt keep its promise of agri reforms...  This is anti-farmer & defeats the purpose of amending Essential Commodities Act. Reform needs a political commitment, not just new laws.
name: Shekhar Gupta
